  "body": "erigon stable v2.56.2\r\nchain: mumbai\r\n\r\n```\r\n[INFO] [01-15|08:05:20.949] RPC server shutting down \r\npanic: sync: WaitGroup is reused before previous Wait has returned\r\n\r\ngoroutine 508149 [running]:\r\nsync.(*WaitGroup).Wait(0x3?)\r\n        sync/waitgroup.go:118 +0x7f\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/erigon-lib/kv/mdbx.(*MdbxKV).Close(0xc0076199e0?)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon-lib@v1.0.0/kv/mdbx/kv_mdbx.go:497 +0x45\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/p2p/enode.(*DB).Close(0xc002708030)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/p2p/enode/nodedb.go:615 +0x65\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/p2p.(*Server).Stop(0xc000004c00)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/p2p/server.go:451 +0xed\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/p2p/sentry.(*GrpcServer).Close(...)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/p2p/sentry/sentry_grpc_server.go:1209\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/eth.(*Ethereum).Stop(0xc000a9d080)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/eth/backend.go:1395 +0x237\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/node.(*Node).stopServices(0x49872e?, {0xc00450ce70, 0x1, 0x465fa0?})\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/node/node.go:216 +0xb2\r\ngithub.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/node.(*Node).Close(0xc00216cf50)\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/node/node.go:159 +0x18b\r\ncreated by github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/turbo/debug.ListenSignals\r\n        github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon/turbo/debug/signal.go:29 +0x273\r\n```\r\n\r\nreported in Discord #general by laibe",
